Introduction

Jang Yi Jeong is a singer-songwriter and producer under HYBE. He is a former member of the boy group HISTORY.

As a producer, he goes by the pseudonym EL CAPITXN and is also the founder of the producing group VENDORS.

He's known for working with BTS, TXT, PSY, NCT, ZeroBaseOne, IU, Sunmi, Heize, and more! His most recent works include: Plave and StayC, Kingdom, Paul Kim, CNBlue's Yonghwa, LOVElution, Yerin, Acid Eyes, and Agust D!
